<paragraph blockId="0.[136,1452,778,1954]" box="[189,418,1823,1846]" pageId="0" pageNumber="166">
<taxonomicName authority="(Jacquin 1760: 25) Brown (1810: 504)" authorityName="Brown" authorityPageNumber="504" authorityYear="1810" baseAuthorityName="Jacquin" baseAuthorityPageNumber="25" baseAuthorityYear="1760" box="[189,418,1823,1846]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Lamiaceae" genus="Leucas" kingdom="Plantae" order="Lamiales" pageId="0" pageNumber="166" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="martinicensis">
<emphasis box="[189,418,1823,1846]" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="166">Leucas martinicensis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection pageId="0" pageNumber="166" type="diagnosis">
<paragraph blockId="0.[136,1452,778,1954]" pageId="0" pageNumber="166">
can be distinguished by its annual habit, ovate to ovate-lanceolate leaves, retrorsely pubescent stem, several axillary whorls along each branch, oblique calyces that are constricted near the throat, with an apical portion reflexed in fruit, calyx teeth as long as the tube, and delicate white corollas barely longer than the calyx and sometimes tinged with red (
<bibRefCitation author="Brown, N. E. &amp; Cooke, T. &amp; Skan, S. A." box="[238,435,1930,1954]" pageId="0" pageNumber="166" pagination="226 - 387" refId="ref1795" refString="Brown, N. E., Cooke, T. &amp; Skan, S. A. (1912) Order CV Labiatae. In: Thiselton-Dyer, W. T. (ed.) Flora capensis. Lovell Reeve, London, pp. 226 - 387." type="book chapter" year="1912">
Brown 
<emphasis box="[319,373,1930,1954]" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="166">et al.</emphasis>
1912
</bibRefCitation>
, 
<bibRefCitation author="Li, H. - W. &amp; Hedge, I. C." box="[446,636,1930,1954]" pageId="0" pageNumber="166" pagination="50 - 299" refId="ref2545" refString="Li, H. - W. &amp; Hedge, I. C. (1994) Lamiaceae. In: Wu, C. Y. &amp; Raven, P. H. (eds.) Flora of China vol. 17. Science Press, Beijing &amp; Missouri Botanical Garden Press, St. Louis, pp. 50 - 299." type="book chapter" year="1994">Li &amp; Hedge 1994</bibRefCitation>
, 
<bibRefCitation author="Morales, R." box="[646,797,1930,1954]" pageId="0" pageNumber="166" pagination="199 - 223" refId="ref2719" refString="Morales, R. (2011) Las labiadas (Lamiaceae) de Guinea Ecuatorial. Anales del Jardin Botanico de Madrid 68: 199 - 223. https: // doi. org / 10.3989 / ajbm. 2288" type="journal article" year="2011">Morales 2011</bibRefCitation>
).
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
